<p>
Summary</p>
<p>
PulsePoint is looking to add a Data Scientist to the engineering team. We need your expertise in machine learning and data mining to help us design and implement algorithms to model and analyze very large data sets.</p>
<p>
The Data Scientist will be responsible for using predictive modeling, statistics, trend analysis, and other techniques to collect, explore and identify the data from internal and external sources. This is an applied research position, and candidates are expected to be able to construct software systems and algorithms to explain or predict customer behavior and solve a variety of business problems (as part of the broader engineering team).</p>
<p>
