<p>
<strong>The Company: PulsePoint</strong><br />
PulsePoint is a content creation &amp; media technology company that brings marketers and consumers together, creating high-value ad impressions.</p>
<p>
PulsePoint owns and operates a network of premium content websites that blend curated content built on a state-of-the-art CMS from more than 500,000 citizen journalists with technology that facilitates meaningful social engagements for both advertisers and publishers. PulsePoint&rsquo;s product and technology suite also includes one of the world&rsquo;s top ad exchanges and a best-in-class audience insight tool.</p>
<p>
PulsePoint is privately-owned and based in New York City, with offices in San Francisco, Los Angeles, Chicago, Austin and London.</p>
